{"tid":1472074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Whatsapp又一廣傳開去post, 點回好？","createTime":"2019-08-14T12:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T12:46:37.000Z","uid":271842,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e97c381eeee44a754cbe227ac2508ad257a42bc1","tid":1472074,"uid":271842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:41:56.000Z","msg":"Whatsapp又一廣傳開去post, 點回好？<br />\n<br />\n轉載👇😠<br />\n特別事項：注意安全      <br />\n                                         <br />\n大家一定要主意，現在班尊貴的學生把鉄路的氣壓閘門放氣，火車的閘門失去氣壓后，隨時可以用手拉開。萬一行車時拉開車門，後果不堪設想，一定死傷無數！<br />\n請廣播比良好市民注意。<br />\n廣傳開去！以免受傷。<br />\n此仍九龍灣港鐵車廠，維修部工程人員傳出，千真萬確。"},{"pid":"d00daa37f22b3c290fe4c4b5719b17462edd3b61","tid":1472074,"uid":1612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:43:41.000Z","msg":"蘋果<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190812/59923258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190812%2F59923258&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=75a01288\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190812%2F59923258&h=ddf42560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190812/59923258</a><br />\n<br />\n有國泰空中服務員向《蘋果》透露，民航局近日不斷刁難國泰及港龍航空的機組人員，如民航局會以第三方身份向機組人員提問安全問題，如機組人員答不上，則會被記下姓名。至於來往中國航點的客機上，也曾出現氧氣瓶內的氧氣在一夜間被耗盡，機組人員懷疑有人針對國泰及港龍航空的客機。<br />\n<br />\n國泰空中服務員林小姐（化名）指，港龍飛往中國航點的航班中的機組人員，受中國民航局處處刁難，「去到大陸航點，就會有民航局嘅人上嚟問安全問題。」她續指，國泰一般都會詢問機組人員安全問題，「無端端有民航局上嚟問野，呢啲情況係其他地方基本上係絕對唔會發生。」<br />\n<br />\n林小姐引述其他港龍機組人員消息指，某些飛往中國航點的航班中，安全用品被消耗至不合正常標準。「機組人員去到大陸某個航點後過夜， 佢哋落機之前check過啲嘢係正常，但係第二日返上機，發現緊急氧氣樽畀人搞過嚟，氧氣樽上面個氣壓計變做0。」她表示，氣壓計正常標準為1,800 psi，機組人員平時也會檢查安全用具標準，即使有消耗亦不會跌至0氧氣。<br />\n<br />\n被問到員工士氣有否遭民航局打壓而下跌時，林小姐表示：「我覺得士氣方面反而會調返轉振奮返，反而我覺得白色恐怖係影響多啲。」<br />\n<br />\n林小姐平時甚少將自己的政見帶到客機上，亦未曾參選機場集會活動，也只會跟志同道合的朋友討論社會情況。"},{"pid":"57c6166db1e1bc87328b734e500c2a86cbe9a138","tid":1472074,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:44:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7d078fd67b8a690a95175d22e4ae019116198db","tid":1472074,"uid":1612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d00daa37f22b3c290fe4c4b5719b17462edd3b61","tid":1472074,"uid":1612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r